          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "It’s a lovely run. Jordan and I talk about all things and manage to run quite a lot faster and further than we had initially thought. The park is beautiful and full of people and dogs. There is a mountain bike track with some bends that people send it through.",
            "link": null
          },
